creator: Technohills Web
descriptionHtml:
Over 1 billion people in India are deaf

We provide learning contents, quizzes, opinions, suggestions, and analytics through sign language.

For the first time in the deaf world, we have created quizzes and cricketing platform through sign language.

We will continue to make significant efforts to preserve the integrity of the game beyond caste, creed and religion.
descriptionShort: This App will help the education gain knowledge.
